{"tid":934761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連尼住會唔會出賣連登仔？邊個鬧過臭雞既好自求多福","createTime":"2018-12-09T13:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T14:03:41.000Z","uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7c5f9e2ed1769399db1e3f853666dd66e25d4a","tid":934761,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"南華早報：呂麗瑤考慮對網上攻擊採取法律行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lui-11_TJlf0_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flui-11_TJlf0_1200x0.png&h=117170fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港田徑代表隊「欄后」呂麗瑤去年報稱被前中學教練性侵，事後她一度遭網友質疑為何不報警，甚至對她作出種種攻擊。《南華早報》報道，呂麗瑤今日表示，正考慮對一連串攻擊她的網上言論採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，呂麗瑤今日獲香港業餘田徑總會頒予53,000元，表揚她雅加達亞運中的表演。她在受訪時談及性侵事件，形容自己情緒已經恢復過來，「但仍有一些人繼續通過互聯網攻擊我」。<br />\n<br />\n她指難以解釋這些網民的行為，「也許除了這種毫無意義的行為，他們無所事事。有些人甚至使用虛假的帳戶，聲稱要促進香港體育運動發局，向我索取資金。」她表示正與經理人商討，「法律行動是其中一個選項」。<br />\n<br />\n呂麗瑤在去年11月30日凌晨在FB撰文，公開自已十四、五歲時被前任教練性侵的經歷，並指自己的剖白是為了喚起公眾對兒童性侵犯的關注。此一事件迅速成為全港焦點，在一開始體壇、官員、議員等一面倒表態支持呂麗瑤的勇敢行為後，網絡上亦出現不少言論，質疑呂麗瑤為何十年後才說出經歷，又批評她婉拒報警的做法，認為是對被指控者不公。<br />\n<br />\n而在今年11月，一名曾任田徑教練的77歲退休人士黃恆，涉於8年前在大埔住所藉詞替女學員按摩，強扯對方內褲非禮，案件經審訊後裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%8D%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/?fbclid=IwAR2qfy2_osg-6CPPYpaWDezrYwbngkKgMbgYQr3atth6jPZea8_Nmue-JDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%2591%2582%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2591%25A4%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%258E%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2qfy2_osg-6CPPYpaWDezrYwbngkKgMbgYQr3atth6jPZea8_Nmue-JDk&d=zI4jTfJbMFlomC76MbivgL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e93b30ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%2591%2582%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2591%25A4%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%258E%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2qfy2_osg-6CPPYpaWDezrYwbngkKgMbgYQr3atth6jPZea8_Nmue-JDk&h=9a4e7e95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%8D%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/?fbclid=IwAR2qfy2_osg-6CPPYpaWDezrYwbngkKgMbgYQr3atth6jPZea8_Nmue-JDk</a>"},{"pid":"faea6f201f5e39ba752e01954e29b5e6db67be67","tid":934761,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"658761a29d4649ac8262bfac1b8b25e7bf84f83c","tid":934761,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"Why左邊張相白咁多"},{"pid":"29d96cf665485f5580de6ff89c44f91089189c59","tid":934761,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"D五官擠埋一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41ae44f9ffe0a3e516e6c575b406c09fcc29450","tid":934761,"uid":217450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"死臭雞落地獄啦淫西"}]}